{"tid":1956542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：Adidas正尋求10億歐元貸款國家援助應對疫情影響","createTime":"2020-04-03T08:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T09:58:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"962e491ce7714b5708ab4f120e7c146572cfcb89","tid":1956542,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情肆虐歐美，有消息人士透露，運動品牌愛迪達（Adidas）正在向德國的一間國有銀行洽談融資，金額約10億到20億歐元之間。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，有知情人士指出，愛迪達正在與德國復興信貸銀行（KfW）就融資進行談判，金額範圍約落在10億歐元到20億歐元之間，最終金額尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n德國為歐洲疫情第3慘重的國家，上月中旬宣佈關閉一切非民生必須商店。德國政府為因應疫情影響，允許繳納不出租金者可延緩繳納，而愛迪達當時表示要暫緩繳納4月房租，遭人詬病濫用。愛迪達本週已表示，會改變先前此項決定。<br />\n<br />\n首席執行官羅斯特（Kasper Rorsted）表示，儘管愛迪達不需要直接的政府支持，但愛迪達和整個經濟都需要信貸。<br />\n<br />\n德國復興信貸銀行於3月23日啟動貸款計劃，以幫助面臨現金流動短缺的公司，大約有2500家公司申請了總額為106億歐元的貸款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3122026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3122026&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=4fc0cc65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3122026&h=23ca68c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3122026</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-02/adidas-is-said-to-seek-more-than-1-billion-euros-of-state-aid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-04-02%2Fadidas-is-said-to-seek-more-than-1-billion-euros-of-state-aid&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=3fc3a6e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-04-02/adidas-is-said-to-seek-more-than-1-billion-euros-of-state-aid</a>"},{"pid":"5c82bfcbae9ce73adf1bcd6161c894c87f9127e6","tid":1956542,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"揾花木蘭啦"},{"pid":"42a03b87f46b39aad55fe74a8d41bcfa59341c79","tid":1956542,"uid":39503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"Adidas不了，以前成日買，依家狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"0651127b91c4272aa945d4b1301abd8984330b7a","tid":1956542,"uid":259716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"搵劉亦菲啦。"}]}